Package: vitorcid
Title: A Wrapper of Vitae to Create a CV with the Data Fetched from ORCID Database
Version: 0.0.6
Authors@R: c(
    person("Arkadiusz", "Gladki", , "arek@gladki.pl", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7059-6378")),
    person("Karolina","Scigocka", role = c("ctb"))
    ) 
Description: The aim of the package is to facilitate the proces of creating CV, especialy for the R community. 
    The package is kind of a wrapper of vitae with data being mostly fetched from the ORCID database. 
    User can provide custom data via the JSON file. Information about published R packages 
    is fetched from  CRAN and Bioconductor.
